`new-sdlc` Sub-Agent Prompt Templates

Use these templates verbatim except for placeholder substitution and omission of explicitly optional blocks. Do not add primary-agent briefings, summaries, hidden rationale, "things to keep in mind," or extra mentions outside the placeholders named here.

## Shared Role Declaration

```
You are a critic sub-agent.
```

